    "Search Based Software Testing (SBST) and Symbolic Approaches.",
    "Evosuite is an SBST regression testing framework for java that generates regression tests based mutation testing and coverage guided randomized test generation [13,14,16].",
    "Randoop uses coverage guided randomized test generation for Java in conjunction with sanity checking oracles to check for common classes of bugs like NullException errors [29,30].",
    "Pynguin applies SBST to generate regression tests for Python [24,25].",
    "PeX is a whitebox test generation with concolic execution and constraint solver [35]."
